 2070 DATA PRONPOS,Pronouns and Possessive Pronouns
 2080 DATA MOD/AUX,Modal verbs and Auxilliary verbs
 2090DATA THE/0,Articles : 'The' or no article
 2100DATA PLCTIME,Prepositions of Place and Time
